entry.title: Israeli Military Poised for Battle for Gaza City
entry.content: Israel began in earnest its dangerous push into Gaza City, piercing the densely populated urban Hamas stronghold with troops and armored vehicles after one of the most intense bombing campaigns of the monthlong war.

entry.title: Foreigners Waiting to Leave Gaza Face Heart-Rending Decisions
entry.content: A daily list of those allowed to exit the besieged enclave is splitting up families and causing bureaucratic headaches.
